{"tid":1751241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"敢怠慢手足，票債定必血償","createTime":"2019-11-24T16:39:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T00:41:07.000Z","uid":104767,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9c90901c2ff64717091a2c6f0d1f6db1aa6f5e65","tid":1751241,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:39:37.000Z","msg":"坦白講，如果唔係外媒當係公投，我一定唔會參與依個毫無認受性嘅選舉。其實為咗場大龍鳳，我哋所有人已經被逼「止暴制亂」，睇吓政府今日幾撚開心？<br />\n<br />\n你班泛民之所以由「賣香港」谷底反彈，全靠前線抗爭者。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>你哋唔少選票只係選民支持前線嘅政治表態，並非你哋應得。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n在此警告所有當選者，你哋嘅票全部流有手足嘅血。如果你哋敢稍有怠慢，甚至割蓆，<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">票債定必血償</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce3147e7a3965d1fbb8d991296bd7e7ce66dba7","tid":1751241,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:40:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed419cb501920d7ec171bc084e4ce3c4f2a53fdb","tid":1751241,"uid":104767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:42:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">敢有怠慢，定必票債血償</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"fbfbd502d7e77f8d64301f3b27e090f36f3f3f29","tid":1751241,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:43:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">敢有怠慢，定必票債血償</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"99c991b66e5495a621a99c6fb6232bf4d57d4f5